column1015: Patient was inpatient 4/15/16-4/22/16. Patient has history of chronic diarrhea. On 4/18/16 patient was tested for clostridium difficile colitis. 4/19/16 it was noted patient was clostridium difficile colitis positive. Patient was placed on oral antibiotics 4/19/16. Patient hospitalized to unrelated disease. Patient was discharged 4/22/16 with oral antibiotics to have in stable condition and will follow-up with physician prn.
Patient was seen in ED 5/21/16. Patient was seen for abdominal pain. Patient was given rectal gel and told to follow-up with physician Monday; and was then discharged.
